    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204820/extras/7ad0621bbfd203f45fc412818cb2bc79.poster.avif?t=1769689980\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204820/extras/7ad0621bbfd203f45fc412818cb2bc79.webm?t=1769689980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从噩梦中醒来后，索菲发现自己被困在一座不断变化的宿舍中，完全不记得自己是如何来到这里的。同时，一个神秘的存在正试图腐蚀她的心智并操纵她的身份。你能否在她失去理智之前带她逃离？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式叙事：</strong> 通过环境叙事展开的深层故事，在多次游玩中逐渐完整呈现。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扭曲的玩法：</strong> 面对烧脑的试炼，观察、选择与谨慎将决定你的命运。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可重复的恐惧：</strong> 不可预测的事件与多种结局，让每一次游玩都充满紧张感。这一次你能成功逃脱吗？</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>渐进式心理恐惧：</strong> 没有廉价的跳吓，只有挥之不去的恐惧、谜团与精神压迫感。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204820/extras/ccbbdcb28396a35db5ceb6212f4c49cb.poster.avif?t=1769689980\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204820/extras/ccbbdcb28396a35db5ceb6212f4c49cb.webm?t=1769689980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
